<DOCNO> APW19980721.0381 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 07/21/1998 21:15:00 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
w1435 &Cx1f; wstm-
r i &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-PapuaNewGuinea-Tsunam     07-21 0904
