<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-Papua New Guinea-Tsunami </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
Body-count worsens as corpses begin falling apart
</HEADLINE>
 &UR; RETRANSMITTING to restore dropped word in slug on ``with'' line &QL; 
 &UR; Eds: RECAPS previous, UPDATES with body-counting process
complicated by deterioration of corpses
 &UR; With BC-Papua New Guinea-Tsunami-Jungle Survivors
 &UR; AP Photos available
 &UR; By ROHAN SULLIVAN &QC; 
 &UR; Associated Press Writer &QC; 

<TEXT>
