<HEADLINE>
Unprecedented mission, but will access be adequate?
</HEADLINE>
 &UR; RETRANSMITS to add editor's note. &QL; 
 &UR; Eds: Lead planned after departure of group from Lisbon, time
uncertain. &QL; 
 &UR; By ELAINE GANLEY &QC; 
 &UR; Associated Press Writer &QC; 

<TEXT>
